  • Method Details

    • launch

      Collection<IStudent> launch​(IInstitute institute, FilterSettings settings)
      Launches its filter, translating provided settings into parameters filter can understand, creates and provides filter with student iterator.
      Parameters:
      institute - Institute with students to be filtered.
      settings - Abstract filter settings which will be translated into more specific ones.
      Returns:
      Collection of students after filtration.
